content: I was thinking of spending around $150 to $200 on the gift. I'm leaning towards the personalized photo album, but I'm not sure if I should splurge on the high-end option or go for something more mid-range. By the way, I've been doing a lot of gift shopping lately, and I've noticed that I tend to spend around $500 per month on gifts for friends and family. Last month, I bought a birthday present for my sister and a housewarming gift for my friend, and then I also attended a baby shower and got a gift for my coworker's baby.
